[[[description]]]
This macro has identical behaviour to the (more common) [`Z_ISREF`](http://phpinternals.net/docs/z_isref) macro. It is simply a micro optimised version of it.

[[[additional_information]]]
This macro also has a counterpart macro, `Z_OPT_ISREF_P`, that accepts a pointer to a zval instead.
